        "gg6z9dQExCR_text": "<p><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">I didn’t think a blanket could make such a difference in my life, but The Fleece Blanket has completely changed how I experience winter. If you’re looking for something to make your evenings at home extra special—or the perfect gift for someone you love—don’t wait. <strong>Trust me, you’ll wonder how you ever lived without it.</strong></span></p>",
